<p>
<note n="0406001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0406001">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】下同</note>
<note n="0407002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0407002">果＝界【宋】【元】【明】</note>
